HEADWORD: Unpeeled
<hw>Un*peeled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <ety>[1st
pref. <ets>un-</ets> (intensive) + <ets>peel</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Thoroughly stripped; pillaged.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> not +
<ets>peeled</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not peeled.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unpeerable</ent>⟦br⟧
